pr_body:
This PR incorporates the following changes:-
1. Add Support for rangeVars
2. EKS commands for creation/deletion of clusters, creation/deletion of nodegroups and resource apply/delete
3. Temporary documentations for EKS

pr_title: Re-arrange directory structure and docs for GKE to support multiple Providers
pr_body:
Signed-off-by: Drumil Patel <drumilpatel720@gmail.com>

This pull request introduces the following changes :

- Move PROJECT_ID to GKE_PROJECT_ID.
- Filename changes to make it more specific to gke(i.e cluster.yaml => cluster_gke.yaml, nodepools.yaml =>nodes_gke.yaml)
- `nodepools` to `nodes` in `\infra` to make it more general.
- Add separate documentation for gke(prombench/docs/gke.md)
- Make prombench documentation more general
